title: Tuition page fields

fields.label: Show next fiscal year
fields.name: show_next_fiscal_year
fields.instructions: If a new school year is starting we might have the tuition/fee information for the year that is starting (this fiscalyear) but not have information for the year after (next fiscal year). Setting this to "Hide next fiscal year" will let us update the tuition/fee information so that it displays the correct information without displaying potentially incorrect information about the year after.
